{"tid":380244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子連割袋鼠頸19刀拍片炫耀　被爆居澳瀋陽人　支那網民震怒：影衰同胞","createTime":"2017-08-30T03:32:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T13:18:17.000Z","uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4292f9a2906bb2c73610f234f0e206a346571d8a","tid":380244,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T03:32:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170830/s00004/1504059701409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170830%2Fs00004%2F1504059701409&d=ZOE%2Fxu9FDZYdKW5NkvQx257TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=515db63f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170830%2Fs00004%2F1504059701409&h=0c3ac1ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170830/s00004/1504059701409</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170830/s00004/e955b9e8eb83713e0cedfd20e757ce1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170830%2Fs00004%2Fe955b9e8eb83713e0cedfd20e757ce1d.jpg&h=2d39f365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一段華裔男子殘殺袋鼠片段在網上瘋傳，引起內地網民廣泛關注，逾一分半鐘片段中，一名身穿間條上衣男子手拿利刀，攻擊一隻躺在地上疑似已受傷的袋鼠，不時割其頸部，見袋鼠掙扎時仍與拍片者調笑，及後更以腳踩住袋鼠連環割頸，其間袋鼠不時發出低吼，最終不支倒下。<br />\n<br />\n片段沒交代拍攝地點及涉事者身分，至日前在內地社交平台朋友圈廣傳後，引來內地網民震怒，大罵對方殘忍，不少人發起人肉搜尋涉事者，認為要將對方繩之以法，又認為男子殘殺袋鼠，估計拍攝地為澳洲，呼籲居澳中國人向當局舉報。<br />\n<br />\n有人分析片段，指操刀者的普通話口音有東北腔，認為很大機會是中國人，狠批就是這種人影衰同胞，更指「罵他是畜牲也是侮辱了畜牲」。<br />\n<br />\n據《今日澳洲》報道，虐殺袋鼠的男子應為一名居於墨爾本的瀋陽人，據其朋友圈的發帖，他疑似是狩獵愛好者，而有關片段最先被發布在北美一個狩獵網站，後來傳回澳洲引起關注，再被上傳到內地社交平台。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指雖澳洲人持槍證下可合法狩獵，惟按法例狩獵行為中不能虐待動物，違者可被判罰款或監禁，而涉事男一刀一刀殘殺的行為已屬非人道方式殺害動物，不少澳洲人已表明會舉報。"},{"pid":"edd76b4c061c7fbaa5494321c848a6038879731b","tid":380244,"uid":8681,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T03:33:47.000Z","msg":"移左民都好 去到幾發達幾文明既國家都係狗改不了吃屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2eb720b1388ab1883ef109c12ebaaa6c6b9704c","tid":380244,"uid":98386,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T03:35:31.000Z","msg":"唔開估正常都會諗係咪支那人"},{"pid":"6c79abb6f96c276e00dd8f5164c5f8400e1996e6","tid":380244,"uid":8048,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T03:36:08.000Z","msg":"絕對唔影衰 根本無乜形象<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee75aab8e6e669f79930ccb068737702aa75d6f","tid":380244,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T03:37:36.000Z","msg":"打獵呢個行為根本垃圾"},{"pid":"e19afaacc0dbedbdf8894e51bb2553d381473734","tid":380244,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T03:38:14.000Z","msg":"雖遠必誅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079cf1fc1c77be6cc3f3812623c0e3c2228cdcee","tid":380244,"uid":84354,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T03:40:48.000Z","msg":"乜支那仲有得影衰咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b88c63be440b0275df6cfcd38dc0b071b725d3f","tid":380244,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T03:41:07.000Z","msg":"影咩衰<br />\n佢根本就係一般支那人"},{"pid":"6f8ad9b4c6e98664449cbceed89af5b19877a0ec","tid":380244,"uid":82532,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T03:46:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://68.media.tumblr.com/30bdc5ef8811db91e59aad4930d84655/tumblr_nhsfepUYTq1qmulzlo1_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F68.media.tumblr.com%2F30bdc5ef8811db91e59aad4930d84655%2Ftumblr_nhsfepUYTq1qmulzlo1_1280.jpg&h=388b1fec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隻揪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66dbba3216fe1aef654917888c965c8129efcebf","tid":380244,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30